# 懵然不知
(pos:形容詞 / 成語)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知、一啲都唔清楚嘅樣貌（量詞：無）
eng:totally ignorant; completely unaware
<eg>
yue:佢對件事懵然不知，仲當住好事嚟講。 (keoi5 deoi3 gin6 si6 maang4 jin4 bat1 zing1, zung6 dong6 zyu6 hou2 si6 lai4 gong2.)
eng:He was completely unaware of the matter and still talked about it as if it were a good thing. [end of text]


